<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy - Requiems API" %>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Last updated: <%= Time.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Requiems API ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
          use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our API platform and services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Account Information</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          When you register for an account, we collect your email address, name, and billing information.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">API Usage Data</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We collect metadata about your API requests including timestamps, endpoint accessed, and response codes.
          We do NOT log the actual request or response data sent through our APIs.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Technical Information</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We automatically collect IP addresses, user agent strings, and other technical information for security and operational purposes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
          <li>Process your transactions and send related information</li>
          <li>Send you technical notices, updates, and support messages</li>
          <li>Monitor and analyze usage patterns and trends</li>
          <li>Detect, prevent, and address technical issues and fraud</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          All data is stored on servers located in the European Union. We implement industry-standard security measures including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>TLS 1.3 encryption for data in transit</li>
          <li>AES-256 encryption for data at rest</li>
          <li>Regular security audits and monitoring</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication mechanisms</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We retain your account information for as long as your account is active. Usage logs are retained for 90 days.
          You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you are located in the European Economic Area, you have the following rights:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Right to access your personal data</li>
          <li>Right to rectification of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
          <li>Right to data portability</li>
          <li>Right to object to processing</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We use the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li><strong>LemonSqueezy:</strong> Payment processing (see their privacy policy)</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Infrastructure and DDoS protection</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          For privacy-related questions or to exercise your rights, contact us at:
          <br/>
          <a href="mailto:eliaz@bobadilla.tech" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">eliaz@bobadilla.tech</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
